<% provide(:title, "5D") %>

<div class="container artist-container">
<br />
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-lg-6">
      <h1 class="dark-on-light">∎ RNL ∎</h1>
      <br /><br />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row justify-content-center body-text">
    <div class="col-sm-6">
      <p>
        RNL is a long-running collaborative project for experimental sound, art, and ideas. Its newest outgrowth has emerged in 2017 as a periodic multimedia anthology with a variable philosophy. In each installment, RNL expands its three ciphers into a new platform for the development of meaning, declaring its thematic direction for that phase.
      </p>
      <hr class="lightline" />
      <p>Here you will find previews of each issue as they become available. Ordering details and additional information will be posted shortly.<br />
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <br /><br />
  <% @rnl_issues.each do |issue| %>
    <div class="rnl-issue">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12 pull-left rnl rnl-title">
          <h5>ISSUE <%= "#{issue.issue_number}: #{issue.title}" %></h5>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4 pull-left rnl rnl-cover">
          <div class="img-fluid">
            <%= image_tag issue.cover_image %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-8 pull-right rnl rnl-pages">
          <div class="img-fluid">
            <p><%= issue.description.html_safe %></p>
            <span class="rnl-background"><%= image_tag issue.background_image %></span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <br />
  <% end %>
  <br />
</div>